snippet.title: Nintendo - Comanche by NovaLogic  ( Super FX 2 )  for Super Nintendo - E3 1995
snippet.description:
Comanche by NovaLogic was one of many Super NES games to be cancelled due to production difficulties. But what was interesting about Comanche - its use of the newly upgrade ( at the time ) SUPER FX 2 chip to accommodate NovaLogic's Voxel technology for full panoramic "3-D" environments.

For more information
--------------------
Comanche: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Comanche_series
Super FX: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Super_FX
